Given I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I select 'Female' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'MRI pelvic floor' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
Then I go to Page 03 and select 'Yes' in Contrast enhanced
Then I select 'Sequences' box
And select 'Oral contrast' checkbox
Then I go to Page 08 of Pelvic MRI
And I click on 'Finding' radio button
And dropdown below 'Finding' is enabled

When I select 'Appendicitis' from the dropdown
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is preselected

And 'Diameter of the appendix' input field is enabled
And 'Wall thickening' input field is enabled
And 'T2w Signal elevation of the intestinal wall' checkbox is enabled
And 'Intraluminal fluid' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cecal wall thickening' checkbox is enabled
And 'Wall edema of adjacent intestinal segments' checkbox is enabled
And 'Appendicolith' checkbox is enabled
And 'Obliteration of the surrounding fat tissue' checkbox is enabled
And 'Thickened mesoappendix' checkbox is enabled
And 'Edema' checkbox is enabled

And 'Perforation' checkbox is enabled
And 'Perityphlitic abscess' checkbox is enabled
And 'Peritoneal involvement' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ileus' checkbox is enabled
And 'Accompanying inflammatory reaction of psoas muscle' checkbox is enabled

When I enter '1' in the input field below 'Diameter of the appendix' checkbox
Then the number is accepted
And 'Length of the appendix' input field is enabled
When I enter '9999' in the input field below 'Diameter of the appendix' checkbox
Then the number is accepted
And 'Length of the appendix' input field is enabled

When I enter '1' in the input field below 'Length of the appendix' checkbox
Then the number is accepted
When I enter '9999' in the input field below 'Length of the appendix' checkbox
Then the number is accepted

When I enter '1' in the input field below 'Wall thickening' checkbox
Then the number is accepted
When I enter '9999' in the input field below 'Wall thickening' checkbox
Then the number is accepted

When I select 'Cecal wall thickening' checkbox
Then '„Arrowhead sign“' checkbox is enabled
And '„Cecal bar sign“' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Perityphlitic abscess' checkbox
Then 'Maximum diameter' input field is enabled

When I enter '1' in the input field below 'Maximum diameter' checkbox
Then the number is accepted
When I enter '9999' in the input field below 'Maximum diameter' checkbox
Then the number is accepted

When I select 'Peritoneal involvement' checkbox
Then 'Adhesions' checkbox is enabled
Then 'Peritonitis' checkbox is enabled




